description: Soul Magic is a magic fantasy role play game and the story surrounds the magic school of Elswyth. Collect ores and magic stones from mining, farming plants and discover through digging. You can also trade resources for Gold Midas, the currency in the world. Soul can be recovered from meditation and will be consumed while conducting activities. We are now running the Admission Carnival. Players who pass the admission quiz will be awarded the Sunstaff, a magic staff that gives you the ability to cast spells!

name: GolfCraft minigolf
creator: OhMyVerse
description: Golfcraft is a minigolf game (made by Eibriel and Pablo) where players can gather materials to craft items and earn resources passively. The game has three main game modes (training, competition, and tournament) which usually consist of sending a ball to a target. Players can also make use of an in-game level editor. https://unve.rs/readGolfCraft

name: Dogebusters HQ
description:
Decentraland plays Pokemon | 
Take a little nostalgic break from your everyday life on MeanGreenDoge's childhood Nintendo Gameboy Advance SP and team up with new friends and take turns every 3 minutes to achieve your goals in the game. | 
 Which team will defeat the top 4 and make Decentraland history? Name your Pokemon and lead it to the winner's podium together.

description: Tominoya is a virtual casino built by Decentral Games. Enjoy non-custodial slots, roulette, and blackjack playable with MANA and DAI.

name: Antrom RPG
creator: @dcl_matt
description: @KnightsOfAntrom, the ultimate role-playing game that will challenge you to farm, craft, and fight your way to the top. Explore a vast and immersive world filled with danger and opportunity at every turn. Gather resources, upgrade your gear, and face off against fearsome enemies as you level up and unlock new abilities and skills. Are you ready to rise to the challenge and become an Antrom legend? Join us and find out!

name: Wilderness P2E
creator: champ
description: Wilderness P2E is a thrilling fantasy role playing game that offers players the chance to earn real rewards through its unique play to earn mechanic. In this game, players can collect utility NFTs that are wearable in the Decentraland metaverse and provide bonuses that can be earned through gameplay. As players explore the vast wilderness and complete quests, they will have the opportunity to earn these NFTs, which can be used to unlock powerful abilities and boost their character's stats. With a wide range of NFTs to collect, players can tailor their character to their own playstyle and dominate in combat. In addition to the exciting gameplay and the chance to earn rewards, Wilderness P2E also offers stunning graphics and a fully immersive world to explore. Join forces with other players and form a party to take on challenging boss battles and conquer the wilderness together. Don't miss out on the chance to experience the unique play to earn mechanic and earn real rewards in Wilderness P2E. Start your journey today and discover the power of utility NFTs. Visit our website at : www.wildernessp2e.com

name: Vroomway®

description: VROOMWAY® is a P2E game in Decentraland, where you can race and battle against your friends — as you collect materials, forge vehicles, and craft upgrades in the Metaverse. An inclusive space for all car lovers to connect and find community!

Inside the headquarters you’ll be able to play games designed and delivered by Sophia herself, with her helpers, Little Einstein and Little Sophia. You’ll earn SOPH Points for your participation – a brand new virtual currency exclusive to the Sophiaverse experience.
